# VitTrade Design System

Before creating or editing UI under `flutter_app/`:

1. Read relevant sections of [DESIGN.md](../../DESIGN.md) (Overview, Colors, Shapes,
   Components, Do's and Don'ts).
2. Map tokens to Dart: `AppColors`, `AppRadii`, `AppSpacing`, `AppTextStyles` from
   `flutter_app/lib/app/theme/`.
3. Reuse `Vit*` shared widgets per [vittrade-ui-guardrails.mdc](vittrade-ui-guardrails.mdc)
   before local scaffolds.
4. Invoke `.codex/skills/ui-ux-pro-max/SKILL.md` only when the batch needs new
   design judgment (execution prompts already specify when).

## Precedence

`AGENTS.md` > active execution prompt > `DESIGN.md` (visual tokens) >
this file > [vittrade-ui-guardrails.mdc](vittrade-ui-guardrails.mdc).

Do not invent colors, radii, spacing, or typography outside theme tokens.
